title: National Parks of New York Harbor: Youth Intern Blogs
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     News     News Releases     Youth Intern Blogs                 Youth-intern blogs       Our interns in the National Parks of New York Harbor youth intern program work with us for 10 weeks every summer. For some of the interns, this is their third summer. Every summer they work at different park, in different jobs. These blogs tell a little about what they are doing in the summer of 2012.
